        ∇

        ∇ {py} StartPython (argfmt program inf outf majorVersion);cmd;pypath;arg
            :Access Public Shared
            :If 0=≢argfmt
                ⍝ Use default argument format: <program> <in> <out>
                argfmt←'''⍎'' ''→'' ''←'''
            :EndIf

            :If 2=⎕NC'py'
            :andif 0≠≢py
                ⍝use given path
                pypath←py
            :else
